data.description: This wonderful home has a very large family room with an optional fireplace on the main level. The kitchen has tons of storage and plenty of workspace. The kitchen opens to the large breakfast nook. The grand master suite is private and has a huge walk-in closet. The master bathroom can be built with a double sink vanity, and either a large walk in shower with two seats and a large linen closet or a small linen closet, separate shower and garden tub. Bedrooms two, three, and loft or optional 4th bedroom, and the second full bathroom finishes out the second level. 2-car garage.
